717
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:26,920
May apat lang sa marketing department!

718
00:51:26,920 --> 00:51:31,590
Pangkaraniwan talaga ang pagkakaroon ng 'U' sa pangalan.

719
00:51:31,590 --> 00:51:33,030
